{
  "stem": "19441.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And because they been so flat, nobody saw that she has there something.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And from time to time, she gave me a little bit of liquid so I should be able to exist.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the same way on the way back, all the five girl-- four girls in the row were special strong girls, because they knew when they will march strongly, they won't look in, because they march.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So four strong girls was, and I was in the middle.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So 80% of the woman was sent to the gas chambers because they was waiting for new arrivals, so they needed the room.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then it take me-- it took me a while.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I started to learn to crawl, from crawling standing up-- like a child-- and slowly my eyesight came together, and slowly my earsight came together.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And just because I was so protected by those girls-- because I helped them, they helped me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this was-- I was always saying to the girls, we have to help each other.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We haven't got anybody who, who wants us to be alive.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Just we want to be-- us to alive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There was a young girl, who was much younger, like I am. and she was blond with blue eyes, and so was her sister.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They was very young girls.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And she said to me-- she was speaking-- she was from a-- like a peasant.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She looked like a peasant and she acted like a peasant because she came from a little village where only one family was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she was exactly like the other peasant girls, but she spoke a peasantly Slovak and Jewish.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So she asked me, tell me, Magda.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Are we going to survive, or we are not going survive?",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
